| **planner** | Produces the plan artifact that the entire BUILD loop depends on. Without it, component-builder has no phase contract. |
| **component-builder** | The only agent that writes production code. Irreplaceable. |
| **integration-verifier** | The only independent proof gate. Without it, builder self-reports PASS with no audit. The Test Honesty Gates catch false-green tests that no other agent checks. |
| **code-reviewer** | The only agent that does spec-compliance checking (MISSING/EXTRA/MISUNDERSTOOD) and PLAN_DEFECT routing. The multi-signal scoring and friction scan are unique. |

